{"tid":597040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全國人大】新浪未投票知結果 搶先報楊曉渡當選","createTime":"2018-03-18T08:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T09:15:12.000Z","uid":3393,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"885c8fa55392aab23492bb14110810064f49fb8b","tid":597040,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180318/large/1521343021_ee8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180318%2Flarge%2F1521343021_ee8d.jpg&h=364efd27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今早全國人大投票選出多名政府高層，各界均引頸以待投票結果。惟當各人大代表仍在投票期間，內地「新浪新聞」於早上10時15分突然推送一則以「楊曉渡當選為中華人民共和國國家監察委員會主任」快訊，引述新華網消息，指楊曉渡當選為中華人民共和國國家監察委員會主任。<br />\n<br />\n雖然外界對楊曉渡的當選並無懸念，但大會在接近11時才陸續公佈投票結果，惟新浪在未完成投票已率先推播國家監察委員會主任由楊曉渡當選，令人費解。<br />\n<br />\n新浪新浪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180318/57962386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180318%2F57962386&d=XdPyjybqQaprp66llt%2BsRcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6ec79c15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180318%2F57962386&h=00a79501\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180318/57962386</a>"},{"pid":"75be0865e67aa6265f8a5a53066746a9e88da796","tid":597040,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"都內定左架啦<br />\n知道有乜奇怪"},{"pid":"b7455339d111112fae7144e16a80fe7acf2358bd","tid":597040,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75be0865e67aa6265f8a5a53066746a9e88da796","tid":597040,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:09:17.000Z","msg":"都內定左架啦<br />\n知道有乜奇怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}